23
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:09,040
But here's the catch. For a comparison to
actually work,

24
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:10,960
you have to be measuring the same thing.

25
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:15,600
So we can compare John's weight to Emily's
