46
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,520
So how do we talk about that?

47
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:33,200
All we have to do is learn the negative
version.

48
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:36,800
Let's take an example. Tokyo Tower is
